{"tid":491530,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]貓b屎眼好臭","createTime":"2017-12-06T15:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T14:51:49.000Z","uid":65343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6a029d37d6333d42df5c45827a36d87042a2a999","tid":491530,"uid":65343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"屋企領養左兩個月大貓仔，黎左幾日。<br />\n尋日開始覺得佢臭，之後有幫佢抹屎眼，屙親屎都抹，抹埋手腳(佢比人捉住好大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n佢啲味好似好左少少。但頭先屙完屎(今日第二次)，幫佢抹完，啲味冇改善過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲嚴重到佢跑過就聞到<br />\n有冇巴絲打門既主人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle左有懷疑係咪肛腺塞，但貓b咁細個會唔會架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果幫佢擠下又得唔得？<br />\n另外想問下抹屎眼應該點抹先令佢冇咁反感呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf7238003e74233f6d0950e4474de544ce985c7","tid":491530,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:10:11.000Z","msg":"問獸醫啦"},{"pid":"5e7f75471abb7eb6543c34c4bd123c77cd3d140b","tid":491530,"uid":47819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"養左20幾年<br />\n無特別搞佢地屎眼個wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed2b312534c3d2d43450fefa717a67007b6539d","tid":491530,"uid":19528,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"屎眼香架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e18a711ea7dc88837f428d1a56a202ba832178","tid":491530,"uid":65343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屎眼香架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算唔香都唔會咁大味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16deff1183303f637b1286335bad1de8